visual_elements.description: Plan view diagram showing a car parked within a rectangular carport space. The diagram indicates two corner columns on the left side, with dimensions labeled as '20' min. open' vertically and 'open' horizontally. The driveway/parking surface is shown at the bottom right side of the carport.

Left side elevation view of a covered parking space with a car underneath. The diagram shows two corner columns supporting a bottom roof system. Vertical clearance is labeled as '7' min. open' and horizontal clearance as '20' min. open'.

Front elevation view of a covered parking space with a car underneath. The diagram shows two corner columns supporting a bottom roof system. Vertical clearance is labeled as '7' min. open' and horizontal clearance as '10' min open'.
